SLEDAI 0-4: Low, 5-8: Moderate, >=9 : High

metadata$SLEDAI_group <- NA
metadata$SLEDAI_group[metadata$`sledai_at_baseline:ch1` <= 4] <- "Low"
metadata$SLEDAI_group[metadata$`sledai_at_baseline:ch1` > 4 & metadata$`sledai_at_baseline:ch1` < 9] <- "Moderate" 
metadata$SLEDAI_group[metadata$`sledai_at_baseline:ch1` >= 9] <- "High"
metadata$SLEDAI_group[metadata$`group:ch1` == "Normal"] <- "HC"

LRB score

source("~/projects/MK_Rcode/setZ.R")
LSP1_gene <- c("CEBPA", "CEBPB", "IL1B", "CCL3", "TNF", "CCL4", "CCL5", "SPP1", "CD7", "MSR1", "ITGAM", "KIT", "CD14", "CSF3R", "IL1R2", "CSF1R", "ITGA1", "ITGA5", "ITGB5", "ITGB1", "CAMP", "THBS1", "C3", "MEFV", "FOS", "CYBB", "CARD9", "IRF7", "OAS3", "NLRP3", "CTSB", "IKBKE", "MPO")
mc <- exprs_annotated - apply(exprs_annotated, 1, median)
LRB_score <- setZ(LSP1_gene ,rownames(exprs_annotated),eset = mc)
hist(LRB_score,50)

Check association between LRB score and SLEDAI

df <- data.frame(value = as.numeric(LRB_score),
                 group = metadata$SLEDAI_group, score = metadata$`sledai_at_baseline:ch1`)
df$group <- factor(df$group, levels = c("HC", "Low", "Moderate", "High"))
df <- df[!is.na(df$group),]

p1 <- ggbetweenstats(
  data = df,
  x = group,
  y = value,
  type = "nonparametric",
  pairwise.comparisons = TRUE,
  p.adjust.method = "fdr") + 
  theme_minimal()

p2 <- ggplot(df, aes(x = group, y = value, fill = group)) +
  geom_boxplot(outlier.shape = NA, color = "black", staplewidth = 0.5, alpha = 0) +
  geom_jitter(aes(color = group), width = 0.2, alpha = 0.8, size = 1.5, shape = 21, fill = "white") +
  labs(title = " ", x = " ", y = " ") +
  theme_classic() + 
  theme(
    legend.position = "none",
    axis.text.x = element_blank(),
    axis.text.y = element_blank(),
    axis.ticks.x = element_line(),
    axis.ticks.y = element_line()
  )

print(p1)

print(p2)

for (i in 1:length(term)) {
  df <- data.frame(ES = as.numeric(es[i,]),
                   group = metadata$SLEDAI_group)
  df$group <- factor(df$group, levels = c("HC", "Low", "Moderate", "High"))
  df <- df[!is.na(df$group),]
  p <- ggbetweenstats(
    data = df,
    x = group,
    y = ES,
    type = "nonparametric",
    pairwise.comparisons = TRUE,
    p.adjust.method = "fdr"
  ) +
    labs(title = term[i],x = "Group", y = "Enrichment score") +
    theme_minimal()
  print(p)
  pp <- ggplot(df, aes(x = group, y = ES, fill = group)) +
  geom_boxplot(outlier.shape = NA, color = "black", staplewidth = 0.5, alpha = 0) +
  geom_jitter(aes(color = group), width = 0.2, alpha = 0.8, size = 1.5, shape = 21, fill = "white") +
  labs(title = " ", x = " ", y = " ") +
  theme_classic() + 
  theme(
    legend.position = "none",
    axis.text.x = element_blank(),
    axis.text.y = element_blank(),
    axis.ticks.x = element_line(),
    axis.ticks.y = element_line()
  )
  print(pp)
}

group_levels <- c("HC" ,"High", "Moderate", "Low")

median_matrix <- sapply(group_levels, function(g) {
  samples_in_group <- which(metadata$SLEDAI_group == g)
  apply(gsva.es[, samples_in_group, drop = FALSE], 1, median, na.rm = TRUE)
})

set.seed(123)
df <- data.frame(
  group = rep(c("A", "B", "C", "D", "E"), each = 30),
  value = c(rnorm(30, mean = 0),
            rnorm(30, mean = 1),
            rnorm(30, mean = 2),
            rnorm(30, mean = 3),
            rnorm(30, mean = 4))
)

ggplot(df, aes(x = group, y = value, fill = group)) +
  geom_boxplot(outlier.shape = NA, color = "black", linewidth = 0.75, staplewidth = 0.5) +
  labs(title = "Whisker Test", x = "Group", y = "Value") +
  theme_minimal()
ggsave("~/projects/2024/RA/GSE88884_RAW/code/boxplot_whisker_test.png", width = 6, height = 4, dpi = 300)

ABC score and SLEDAI

df <- data.frame(ABC_score = as.numeric(ABC_score),
                 group = metadata$SLEDAI_group, score = metadata$`sledai_at_baseline:ch1`)
df$group <- factor(df$group, levels = c("HC", "Low", "Moderate", "High"))
df <- df[!is.na(df$group),]

t1 <- ggbetweenstats(
  data = df,
  x = group,
  y = ABC_score,
  type = "nonparametric",
  pairwise.comparisons = TRUE,
  p.adjust.method = "fdr") + 
  theme_minimal()

t2 <- ggplot(df, aes(x = group, y = ABC_score, fill = group)) +
  geom_boxplot(outlier.shape = NA, color = "black", staplewidth = 0.5, alpha = 0) +
  geom_jitter(aes(color = group), width = 0.2, alpha = 0.8, size = 1.5, shape = 21, fill = "white") +
  labs(title = " ", x = " ", y = " ") +
  theme_classic() + 
  theme(
    legend.position = "none",
    axis.text.x = element_blank(),
    axis.text.y = element_blank(),
    axis.ticks.x = element_line(),
    axis.ticks.y = element_line()
  )

print(t1)
print(t2)
